{"id": "art-25131", "label": "Art. 25131", "title": "Art. 25131", "slug": "art-25131", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1845768747\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1615\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1845768747\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>31</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1489758365\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1614\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1489758365\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În termen de 45 de zile de la data efectu&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span> proiectului comun de fuziune\ntransfrontalier&#259;, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>28</sup>, orice creditor a c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span>\neste anterioar&#259; acestei date <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nnescadent&#259; la aceast&#259; dat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncare este <span class=SpellE>nemul&#355;umit</span> de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iile</span>\nacordate prin proiectul comun de fuziune transfrontalier&#259; notific&#259;\nsocietatea participant&#259; la fuziune al c&#259;rei creditor este în vederea\nacord&#259;rii de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> adecvate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2108920476\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1613\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2108920476\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În termen de 15 zile de la împlinirea termenului\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (1), societatea transmite creditorului oferta privind\nacordarea de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1885405461\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1612\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1885405461\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care creditorul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1)\nnu consider&#259; adecvate <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iile</span> acordate,\nse poate adresa <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> pentru obligarea <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> la acordarea de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span>\nadecvate, dac&#259; creditorul <span class=SpellE>dovede&#351;te</span>, în mod\nrezonabil, c&#259; fuziunea afecteaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;ansele</span>\nde acoperire a <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;ei</span>. <span class=SpellE>Garan&#355;iile</span>\nsunt acordate sub <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ia</span> ca fuziunea s&#259;\nproduc&#259; efecte.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1009228618\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1611\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1009228618\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Cererea se depune, în termen de 3 luni de la data\nefectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span> potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>28</sup>, la oficiul\nregistrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> de la sediul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> participante la fuziune, care, în\ntermen de 3 zile de la data depunerii, o <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span>\nîn registru <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> o înainteaz&#259; tribunalului în\na c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se afl&#259; sediul\nsocial al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> participante la\nfuziune. La cerere se anexeaz&#259; dovada notific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nîn vederea constituirii de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dup&#259; caz, oferta <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.\nHot&#259;rârea <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> este executorie <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> este supus&#259; numai apelului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1368048031\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1610\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1368048031\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Cererea creditorului se judec&#259; de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu\nprec&#259;dere. Dac&#259; sunt formulate mai multe cereri, acestea se\nconexeaz&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2126675593\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1609\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2126675593\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Certificatul prealabil fuziunii transfrontaliere poate\nfi emis numai dac&#259; societatea prezint&#259; dovezi privind constituirea <span\nclass=SpellE>garan&#355;iilor</span> potrivit proiectului comun de fuziune sau\nca urmare a notific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ori\npotrivit hot&#259;rârii <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_206042396\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1608\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_206042396\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nromân&#259; este <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legea</i>\naplicabil&#259; cererilor creditorilor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nparticipante la fuziune formulate potrivit alin. (3), iar tribunalul în a\nc&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se afl&#259; sediul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> participante la fuziunea\ntransfrontalier&#259; este <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\ncompetent&#259; s&#259; <span class=SpellE>solu&#355;ioneze</span> cererile\nacestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2114326964\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1607\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2114326964\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Pe o perioad&#259; de 2 ani de la data la care produce\nefecte fuziunea transfrontalier&#259;, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>36</sup> alin. (3), orice cerere a oric&#259;rui creditor care <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span> o <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span>\nanterioar&#259; datei efectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nproiectului de fuziune <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nescadent&#259; la\nacea dat&#259;, în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu acea <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span>,\npoate fi adresat&#259; <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> competente în a\nc&#259;rei <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> teritorial&#259; a\navut sediul social societatea participant&#259; la fuziune al c&#259;rei\ncreditor este.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1183444308\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1606\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1183444308\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prin <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ie</span> de la\nprevederile art. 172 alin. (1) lit. d), <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nalin. (1)-(8) sunt aplicabile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>.</span></p>"}